{"tid":1924244,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖，詳盡分析) 三個訊號話俾你知大市已經見底","createTime":"2020-03-13T14:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T06:08:56.000Z","uid":190748,"like":9,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1a32c07a072c0b43271e46ae3544c903d2f8313b","tid":1924244,"uid":190748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:40:11.000Z","msg":"大家好，又係我十年牛市。<br />\n今日恆指低位狂抽1600點，結束一連10幾日嘅大跌市，出現咁多位散戶期待已久嘅大奇積日。<br />\n以下依三個訊號話比大家知大市見底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 1. 今日出現大陽燭，而且成交達到2000億。意味着有好強大嘅買盤係低位出現，大大力咁掃上去，依個同阿爺下星期降準救市有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T3SBR20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT3SBR20.png&h=511dbc2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 嚟緊19號有議息，市場預料會再到減息，刺激升市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 連茶記啲師奶都話大跌市，根據連登理論，都唔炒股嘅人都討論大跌市，就係升市嘅開端<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期一大家預計會升幾多點，一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35556d7b5a768d215766252b92b878139f3c6687","tid":1924244,"uid":262116,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:42:51.000Z","msg":"個個都認屎認屁爭住入匯豐<br />\n你覺得會係見底咩"},{"pid":"af8f1d91c618fdebe727ccf3e5eec264484d6822","tid":1924244,"uid":51790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"個個都諗住見底衝入去撈貨<br />\n即係未見底囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09420bd65d06be92722548b69ad47c302747b949","tid":1924244,"uid":14230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"979bbf247fbba7fc1b83157a8e261dc47c710c27","tid":1924244,"uid":263618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:44:17.000Z","msg":"point 3 ..... <br />\nmeans will further fall lor"},{"pid":"6a